sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer
    participant MobileApp
    participant SupabaseAuth
    participant BackendAPI

    Customer->>MobileApp: Enter credentials
    MobileApp->>SupabaseAuth: signInWithPassword(email, password)
    SupabaseAuth->>BackendAPI: Validate credentials
    BackendAPI-->>SupabaseAuth: Return session
    SupabaseAuth-->>MobileApp: Session received
    MobileApp->>MobileApp: Store session & update auth state
    MobileApp-->>Customer: Redirect to home screen